{"tid":1443393,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"突發：警方呼籲深水埗在場人士盡快離開","createTime":"2019-08-11T08:11:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T08:24:13.000Z","uid":41404,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b65d5fc0b9729acab113bec27f5b574189798641","tid":1443393,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T08:11:25.000Z","msg":"電台及電視台當值宣布員注意：<br />\n <br />\n請盡快播出下列消息，並在適當時間重播：<br />\n<br />\n     今日（八月十一日）下午三時許，深水埗的示威者佔用長沙灣道的行車線。在場人士現正參與「未經批准的集結」，屬違法行為，現場交通受到影響。<br />\n      <br />\n     警方呼籲在場人士盡快離開，並提醒駕駛人士留意最新交通情況。 <br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2019年8月11日（星期日）<br />\n香港時間16時01分"},{"pid":"a896d70b2ab7d4311d684b1bc0fc6f82e05299e8","tid":1443393,"uid":108236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T08:12:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7639dc40a8304294577f54e92aad02038e030f2","tid":1443393,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T08:13:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"deab423498d3ae3aaba5fa6bfc9162bb6078c535","tid":1443393,"uid":78470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T08:13:32.000Z","msg":"想趕人去北角圍打<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6e2d5e4823432a5f191572d17780760e9a526e7","tid":1443393,"uid":283071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T08:24:13.000Z","msg":"突發  一齊立即去圍住呢個停車場<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1443414\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1443414</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}